.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

Sport: sailing, skiing, biathlon, swimming, soccer
Nationality: british, danish, german, norwegian, swede
Beverage: beer, coffee, milk, tea, water
Birthday: sailingmaster, october, december, september, june
Pet: cat, bird, dog, fish, horse
1. Nationality:british == Sport:biathlon
2. Nationality:swedish == Pet:dog
3. Nationality:danish == Beverage:tea
4. Sport:skiing is on the left of Sport:swimming
5. Sport:skiing == Beverage:coffee
6. Birthday:december == Pet:bird
7. Sport:soccer == Birthday:october
8. Beverage:milk is in the middle
9. Nationality:norwegian is on the far left
10. Birthday:june is on the left or right of Pet:cat
11. Pet:horses is on the left or right of Birthday:october
12. Birthday:sailingmaster == Beverage:beer
13. Nationality:german == Birthday:september
14. Nationality:norwegian is on the left or right of Sport:sailing
15. Birthday:june is on the left or right of Beverage:water

